Requirements:

- Expat XML Parser library version 1.95.8 or newer (http://expat.sourceforge.net/)
- CURL library 7.15.1 or newer (http://curl.haxx.se/)

Description:

The Reelblog plugin (based on RSS Reader plugin) provides a simple OSD menu based user interface
for reading special reelblog feeds.
 
The current code is heavily reusing the VOD plugin by Olivier Jacques and the RSS Reader plugin by Rolf Ahrenberg.
Huge thanks to the original author!
